txt.en: Defeat Stone-trolls in the Bruinen Gorges

There are Stone-trolls settled in the Bruinen Gorges of the Trollshaws, though they are rarely seen but at night.\n\nWhile you are in the Bruinen Gorges, you should deal with the Stone-trolls which have settled there.
